</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/7305-4049">Joseph Rizzi</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">3 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Patent pending - Having a one atmosphere dome on the sea floor allow drilling multiple wells at the same time. you can also use the seas own pressure to assist in the extraction of oil. Currently working on California government offices but they are unwilling to open their minds to new ideas. If anyone is interested I have complete details. </div>
