<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_3653"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3653-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3653">Invest in alternative fuels and clean energy&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/6752-4049">jmylett</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">4 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">I think the time has come to invest in alternative fuels, clean energy technology, and curb our dependence on oil. Wind, Solar, Bio-Fuels, and Fuel Cells, my be something to consider and invest in our country.</div>
